                     <interp inst="t17810711-26-person513" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>

               <p>He enquired of me where Mr. Summerfield lived.</p>

               <p>(The prisoner did not say any thing in his defence.)</p>

